text: Lycée Alain is a senior high school/sixth form college in Le Vésinet, Yvelines, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. It is named after Émile Chartier, a.k.a. "Alain"."Qui est Emile Chartier, dit "Alain" ? " Lycée Alain. Retrieved on September 2, 2016. ==References== ==External links== * Lycée Alain Category:Lycées in Yvelines
